{"tid":2346577,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國「制裁」NBA莫利，可以去到幾盡？ 76人都被禁播 | 沈旭暉","createTime":"2020-12-30T10:52:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-30T12:26:20.000Z","uid":48083,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"399708c7dda1ace77dc7ac0cdc3329aca229ae22","tid":2346577,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T10:52:16.000Z","msg":"⋯⋯去年曾發言支持香港抗爭的火箭總經理莫利，成為中國示範「槍打出頭鳥」的對象，最終在本季離開，表明絕不後悔，然後加盟另一支球隊76人。結果中國「制裁」如影隨形，騰訊居然立刻叫停直播76人的賽事，方丈指數，令人歎為觀止。同時火箭也依然享有同一待遇。至於整個NBA賽事本身，則繼續被中央台停播。<br />\n<br />\n⋯⋯所以中國制裁莫利，只是象徵性的，真正目標是樹立「親共樣板」，予以統戰，賦予經濟紅利，再用他們來影響其他球員。這就是香港的「統戰周柏豪模式」，而在NBA，已經落水的最著名球星自然是 LeBron James；在英超，反面教材自然是阿仙奴的奧斯爾，可以比喻為香港的「王宗堯模式」。而我們不得不承認，對個人來說，中國這一著，確實具有相當威力⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/posts/45575823\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.patreon.com%2Fposts%2F45575823&d=%2BG0gz%2BKtHqwTrAvvvLwqSBX1SmvCJyfLMOcbfj5ioUM%3D&h=e6951c1d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.patreon.com/posts/45575823</a>"},{"pid":"2ab89894075934aa7d84e42061cdd48eb1534a46","tid":2346577,"uid":73381,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T10:53:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4qpVMNn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4qpVMNn.png&h=f10fa2f7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8a834b18f908412ae8eccd24a72817e2b60bbc38","tid":2346577,"uid":92299,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T11:03:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4UZCfJ8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4UZCfJ8.png&h=d6778bee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b952595ac8d1cf83c4ddbe339c83ce5a2af1108d","tid":2346577,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T11:05:54.000Z","msg":"二樓jm9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcdb3a0b5cea5049387d46fc44c5dff3dd23337c","tid":2346577,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,